## 🚀 **USAGE EXAMPLES**

### **Authentication**
```bash
# Login
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/auth/login" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"email": "admin@example.com", "password": "password"}'
```

### **Create Agent**
```bash
# Create new agent
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/agents" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "Customer Service Bot", "description": "Handles customer inquiries"}'
```

### **Test Licensing**
```bash
# Check license status
curl -X GET "http://localhost:8000/licensing/status" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>"
```

### **Create Training Workspace**
```bash
# Create training workspace
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/training-lab/workspaces" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "Customer Service Training", "agent_id": 1}'
```

